{"tid":1355134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加快！打正旗號：反恐襲 反警黑 劍指政權","createTime":"2019-07-23T09:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:44:27.000Z","uid":280368,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc2888abe14fe78963e0c71587749c3344c51b6","tid":1355134,"uid":280368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"我地唔係去搞事，我地唔係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n721晚元朗發生<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐怖襲擊</span>，令香港市民生命安全受威脅<br />\n有視頻顯示警察無能力再保護市民，甚至<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見死不救</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有議員話中聯辦曾動員黑社會<br />\n<br />\n所有香港人：<br />\n反對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">恐怖襲擊</span></span><br />\n反對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">警黑合作</span></span><br />\n反對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">干涉香港內政</span></span>"},{"pid":"4aca7d90b579f7d416f68fc8e5b3cdd0f12bfa55","tid":1355134,"uid":280368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"光復元朗係我地嘅行動方式<br />\n<br />\n剑指政權才是我們的目的！<br />\n<br />\n唔可以俾人覺得我地係去打鬥，我地有合理理由去元朗<br />\n亦係時代革命嘅重要運動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大力合理宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反恐襲 反警黑</span></span>"},{"pid":"f56337d5dd497fe3dd00c9f58bc2d959c81f9e30","tid":1355134,"uid":280368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"899e0472bf7d910a3e04cad8cb88abc00aaeface","tid":1355134,"uid":280368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fee06ffa39cb5759199bc2244fd51f4214f6256b","tid":1355134,"uid":280368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9574bd962b71d7bcdfb985de6a56e812923950d5","tid":1355134,"uid":280368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:15:14